OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fa few light showers this evening.
OL,7,FBecoming largely dry with some clear
OL,8,Fspells developing, especially late in
OL,9,Fthe night. Breezy and feeling cool.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FSunny spells for many,
OL,12,Fthough cooler than recent days.
OL,13,FLargely dry with occasional showers
OL,14,Faffecting Kent. Breezy, especially
OL,15,Falong coasts. Chilly overnight with
OL,16,Fisolated rural frosts possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
